#: pdfarranger/pdfarranger.py:315
msgid ""
"PDF Arranger is a small python-gtk application, which helps the user to "
"merge or split pdf documents and rotate, crop and rearrange their pages "
"using an interactive and intuitive graphical interface. It is a frontend for "
"pikepdf."
msgstr ""
"PDF Arranger es una pequeña aplicación python-gtk, que ayuda al usuario a "
"fusionar o dividir documentos pdf y a rotar, recortar y reorganizar sus "
"páginas usando una interfaz gráfica interactiva e intuitiva. Es una interfaz "
"para pikepdf."

